text: Novokilmetovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Baymurzinsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 151 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 35 km from Mishkino, 5 km from Baymurzino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Novokilmetovo
